where $g^i_{jk}=(p_{D_i}g_i,\xi_{jk})$, $j=1,2,\cdots $, $k=1,2,\cdots,r_j$, $i=1,2,\cdots,p$ and
$E_{\alpha,\beta}(z):=\sum\limits_{i=0}^\infty
{\frac{z^i}{\Gamma(\alpha i+\beta)}},$ $\mathbf{Re}{\kern 2pt}\alpha>0, ~\beta,z\in \mathbf{C}$
