For any $z_*\in H^{\frac{1}{2}}(\Gamma)$, denote by $\left(\cdot,\cdot\right)_{H^{1/2}(\Gamma)}$ the inner product of space $H^{\frac{1}{2}}(\Gamma),$  we then see that
